* 현재진행형

- 현재의 한 시점에서 진행 중인 동작이나 상태를 표현
ex) I am reading a really good book at the moment
ex) You are working very hard today

-변화하고 있는 상황을 나타낼 때 사용
get, become(~되다) / change(변화하다) / increase, grow(증가하다)
/decrease, fall(감소하다) / begin, start(시작하다) 등의 동사와 주로 사용.
ex) Is your English getting better?
ex) Is your English improving?
ex) I am beginning to enjoy it.



* 현재시제

- 일반적인 사실이나 반복적인 행동을 나타낼 때 사용
ex ) He drives a bus.

* 빈도부사

- always(항상)/ almost always(거의 항상) / usually(대게)/ ofter(자주)
/sometimes (가끔)/ seldom, rarely, hardly ever(드물게) / never(전혀)

- be동사 뒤에 do 앞에 위치
ex) I was never very good at math
ex) He often makes silly decisions
ex) Henry is always on time -> Is Henry always on time?
ex) You usually have milk in your coffee? -> do you usally have milk in your coffee?
ex) We don't usually get up before nine on Sunday.
(usually 와 dont 위치 변경 가능)
ex) Public transport isn't always reliable
(always는 무조건 부정어 not 뒤에 위치)
ex) Dog food doesn't always taste good.
(alwyas는 무조건 부정어 not 뒤에 위치)